https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_css_pagination.asp - 페이지

https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_css_star_rating.asp - 별점 매기기

https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_js_trigger_button_enter.asp - 검색
